{
  "texts": [
    "In the first step of the process, users have to upload their data onto the platform.",
    "The input data can be the structure of a small molecule, the structure or name of the molecular target, or their chemical properties.",
    "The second step, called the generation phase, involves running the platform with many generative models operating in parallel to create new structures.",
    "These new structures pass through various filters.",
    "Then, in the third step, the molecular structures are evaluated using multiple sets of reward and scoring modules, where the properties of the generated structures based on predefined criteria are evaluated."
  ]
}